	not for the fonts themselves.

	* nf/Garuda*.sfd:
	  - Bump font version to 004.000
	* nf/Kinnari*.sfd:
	  - Bump font version to 003.000
	* nf/Norasi*.sfd:
	  - Bump font version to 006.000

