	TlwgTypewriter: Add Apostrophe mod & Minus mod for Patani Malay.

	* tlwg/TlwgTypewriter*.sfd:
	  - Add U+02BC apostophemod glyph.
	  - Add U+02D7 minusmod glyph.
	  - Bump font version to 002.007.

