2014-06-26  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <theppitak@gmail.com>

	Laksaman: Add special high variant glyphs support.

	* sipa/Laksaman*.sfd:
	  - Add high Nikhahit, high Maitaikhu, high Yamakkan glyphs.
	    From normal glyph, scaled 67%, expand stroke by 9 (15 for bold),
	    move so AboveMark Mark anchor is placed at Sara II's
	    Above Mark Base anchor.
	  - Remove AboveMark Mark anchor from normal glyphs,
	    and AboveBase Mark anchor from high variants.
	  - Bump font version to 3.04: 2014-06-26.

