	  - 'ccmp' Thai General Composition:
	    - Add uni0E4E to class 5 so it gets converted to high variant.
	    - Add lookups to convert marks to high variant when it comes
	      after all above-base characters and their converted variants.
	  - Add AboveMark base anchor for normal & low tone marks,
	    normal & high Maitaikhu, high Nikhahit, normal & high Yamakkan.
