	  - Clear OS/2 Panose and use defaults.

2009-07-02  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* tlwg/Makefile.am, +tlwg/Purisa-[Bold]Oblique.sfd:
	Add oblique faces for Purisa.

	* tlwg/Purisa-Bold.sfd: Fix some overlaps.

