2009-06-24  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* tlwg/TlwgMono*.sfd:
	  - Correct direction for THO THONG, SARA AA, SARA AM, LAKKHANGYAO,
	    THAI DIGIT ONE glyphs.
	  - Re-apply autohings without diagonal hints (diag hints cause glitch
	    in some glyphs like asterisk).
	  - Manually add diag hint to DIGIT FOUR for TlwgMono.sfd.
	  - Bump font version to 001.013: 2009-06-24.

