	Supphachoke Santiwichaya <mrchoke@opentle.org>.
	Prefer mkfontscale in install scripts.

2003-07-22  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* configure.in, Makefile.am:
	Prefer mkfontscale if present, and use it for both type1 and ttf.
	Always use -e option for mkfontdir.

2003-07-03 Chanop Silpa-Anan <chanop@debian.org>
	* *.sfd :
	Change glyph names from PUA to Unicodename.variant.
	Glyph 0x007f has name .notdef and unicodename U+007F.
	* Norasi*.sfd:
	Glyph DEL locates at 0xff with unicodename U+F17B.
	Thaipaiyalnoi bug in Norasi-Bold.

